title: It’s the Economy Stoopid!

description:
Programming Description: Charlamagne Tha God debates topical stories with comedians W. Kamau Bell and Michael Blackson. CNN Anchor Don Lemon also stops by for a candid conversation. Plus, comedian Chico Bean asks everyday people if we are in a recession.
